   neighbor 10.0.1.2 peer group SPINE_OVERLAY
   neighbor 10.0.1.2 remote-as 4259840011
   !
   vlan 103
      rd 10.0.2.3:10103
      route-target both 11:10103
      redistribute learned
   !
   vlan 203
      rd 10.0.2.3:10203
      route-target both 11:10203
      redistribute learned
   !
